Rating: 4
Loved this recipe! I am rather amused by all the people who have tried to make it more flavorful! Evidently they don't really want Shepherd's Pie, they want a casserole. Shepherd's Pie is supposed to be on the bland side. Most recipes for this dish don't even call for the celery and carrots and peas. You're missing the whole idea when you add lots of flavorings, mushrooms, etc.. You can do that if you like, and it's probably very good, but then you shouldn't present it to anyone as being Shepherd's Pie.

